Subject: Not Getting Monthly Report
Description: Hello. We typically get an audit report delivered on the 1st of every month. This month we did not get it. Can someone please help me figure out why we did not receive the report. Thank you
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
Monthly report was not received in email.

Cause
Email server settings had changed from the Auditor server settings which led to failed emails.

Resolution
Updated the email settings in Enterprise Auditor and ran the report jobs again.
We were able to verify that the emails were sent and received successfully.
